
    THE son of late Black Consciousness icon Steve Biko appeared
in the Cape Town Magistrate's Court on Thursday for the alleged assault of his
wife. Businessman Hlumelo Biko, whose mother is activist, doctor
and businesswoman Mamphela Ramphele, allegedly assaulted his wife in Camps Bay.Prosecutor F Naidoo read a charge of assault with intent to
